-- Erdogan Says Eight Killed in Turkish Factory Explosion
-- B y   S e l c a n   H a c a o g l u
-- 2013-01-30T10:35:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-30/erdogan-says-eight-killed-in-turkish-factory-explosion.html
The explosion occurred at a
galvanizing factory in southern city of Gaziantep, Prime
Minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan says during an address to his
lawmakers in parliament in Ankara.
* A boiler exploded at the factory, NTV television says, citing
